strings: <voice_0x01001814><se_low>Chen Mui: Hm? You want to hear my story once again?
<voice_0x01001815><se_low>Chen Mui: What? Er...are you quite sure? I was primed to tell you the tragic and moving tale.
<voice_0x01001816><se_low>Chen Mui: Good, good! Then make sure you're sitting comfortably, and I'll begin...

<voice_0x01001817><se_low>Chen Mui: ...Well, that's the end.
Phew! I'm spent!
